com.arangodb.springframework.repository.query

Class ArangoParameterAccessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.arangodb.springframework.repository.query.ArangoParameterAccessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<Object>, org.springframework.data.repository.query.ParameterAccessor

    public class ArangoParameterAccessor
extends Object
implements org.springframework.data.repository.query.ParameterAccessor
    The main class used to access parameters of a user-defined method. It wraps ParametersParameterAccessor which catches special parameters Sort and Pageable, and catches Arango-specific parameters e.g. AqlQueryOptions
